Package abyss.pathing

Enum Class ClipFlag

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ClipFlag>
abyss.pathing.ClipFlag
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ClipFlag>, Constable
public enum ClipFlag extends Enum<ClipFlag>
BW = Actually blocks a tile when step is processed BP = Blocks projectiles PF = Pathfinder only takes these flags into consideration when generating a path PFBW = Blocks tiles for both walk steps and the pathfinder
